attributes.name: Hard Candy Tabs – AK-47 (Hybrid-Sativa): Green Lemonade
attributes.body: Bhang’s delicious hard candy infused with SWOP’s AK-47 harvest. AK-47 is one of our favorite strains because of its calm, focused and happy effect. The prevalent terpenes are myrcene and pinene, followed by caryophyllene. The near equal amounts of pinene and myrcene duke it out to balance between myrcene’s sedative and muscle relaxing effects and pinene’s clear headed and focused effects. The caryophyllene may aid in a bit of pain relief as well for some patients. This strain is great for patients dealing with daytime anxiety, stress or depression.

attributes.name: Organic Dark Chocolate Bar – Purple Kush (Indica)
attributes.body: Bhang’s delicious organic dark chocolate infused with SWOP’s Purple Kush. Our Purple Kush has a musty/earthy/floral smell with a calming, happy effect. PK’s main terpenes are myrcene, ocimene, and pinene. Myrcene as we all know by now effects the permeability of cell walls, making more cannabinoids available to more receptors, and carries its own sedative and muscle relaxing effects. Ocimene is used for an anxiolytic and for balance. Pinene keeps everything clear-headed and focused. We suggest Purple Kush for anxiety, muscular pain, and for our bi-polar patients to balance out.
